<h2 class="bold font-l">Peter's Company Suck-Up</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Upon becoming president of El Dorado Cigarettes, Peter is given one of these, which turns out to in fact be a robot. </p>
</div>
